text: Iltayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yangatausky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 153 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Maloyaz, 6 km from Yangatau. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Iltayevo
